<D>__{the hell with "useful" those critters'd y turn you into a food item! little popsicle things! ya hear me? one day you're a big ole whale and the next minute, funfood!!}
<C>__{mumble}
<D>__{but if your grandpappys saw them and they survived, maybe they're not so fierce. seal #1 you calling me a liar son? seal #2 he's calling your grandpappy a liar. and you know what, maybe he's right. seal#1 why you. flop over here and say that!}
