<C>__{the adelies }
<D>__{woooaaaahhh!!}
<A>__{the ice pad flips, flinging them into the water like a handful of peanuts.}
<B>__{in the sea}
<A>__{the penguins head for shore , swimming for their lives. loveday, thrashing and wheezing, is unable to keep up.}
<C>__{mumble}
<P>__{(stops)}
