<B>__{later}
<A>__{he's getting closer. the ships are only half a mile away when something rises from the deep, threatening to engulf him: a huge net, teeming with fish. mumble shoots out of the way, just avoiding being caught as. up ahead the great net full of fish breaks the surface of the water and is winched on board.}
